'''Ring*Con 2009''' is an upcoming convention in Germany, scheduled to take place from [[2 October|October 2]] to [[4 October|October 4]], in the Maritim Hotel in Bonn. 

==Guests==
In addition to several stars from ''[[wikipedia:Harry Potter (film series)|Harry Potter]]'' and ''[[wikipedia:Twilight (2008 film)|Twilight]]'', the following stars are confirmed to attend:

* [[Lori Dungey]]
